			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>&#8220;No Show,&#8221; the former Air Force Flight Surgeon joins us again, with the planned second interview.  Here, he talks about &#8220;naughty pilots&#8221; and the things that we do to ourselves that can affect our flying.  You can download the podcast here:<a href="http://media.libsyn.com/media/flyingpilot/FPP016.mp3"><img src="images/podcast.jpg" alt="Podcast" /></a></p>
